OL,4,CBrewdog boss vows to learn after 'toxic
OL,5,Cculture' criticism
OL,6, A co-founder of Brewdog has promised to
OL,7, listen and learn from savage criticism
OL,8, of the beer company by 60 ex-staff.
OL,10,FJames Watt told the BBC claims of a
OL,11,F"culture of fear" and "toxic attitude"
OL,12,Fwere tough to hear, but said they would
OL,13,Fhelp make him a better chief executive.
OL,15,FIn an open letter, signatories said a
OL,16,F"significant number" of former staff
OL,17,Fhad "suffered mental illness as a
OL,18,Fresult of working at Brewdog".
OL,20,FMr Watt said it is clear some things
OL,21,Fwent wrong: "We genuinely apologise."
